name: Che
description: '''Chase Shaun Mitchell''' (born August 29, 2006), known by his stage name '''Che''', is an American rapper, singer, songwriter, and producer from [[Atlanta]], [[Georgia (U.S. state)|Georgia]]. He first gained traction in late 2021 through viral tracks on [[TikTok]] and streaming platforms, particularly for his song "Agenda", and later saw additional success in 2024 with "Miley Cyrus" and "Pizza Time".
